<br>
<br>
Agro procs &gt; dps<br>
<br>
13/20 of the sapper is top notch...ok...so what is the skybreaker is better dps? I would NOT main hand that weapon.<br>
<br>
Some people forget...in some guild you will have from 2-8+ warlords...Normally the MT and ST would keep their high agro procing weapons going. The other warlords need to bag the likes of the willsaper to agro pulling agro. A tank using a willsaper who is not supposed to be pulling agro is careless and should not be there. Of course, if you want to stay high on the agro list..then put in a lower taunting proc weapon...or just mainhand the likes of willsaper for 1 proc or so to keep up there on hate list.<br>
<br>
Personally I think if you are trying to hold agro....willsaper is far better than skybreaker. but then again I do not consider myself uber or have top notch items...I have a basic warlord kit. I am more than happy with willsaper..and I consider it to be prety much an end game item for me.<br>
<br>
If you are counting on DPS to hold your agro..then your wizzies and rogues will be tanking...not the warlord.<br>
<br>
