<br>
If the Willsapper was a 7/20 wep or something then yeah it would be a lot more questionable as a MT weapon - however it's 13/20 which is a pretty good ratio.<br>
<br>
A high taunt proc weapon doesn't mean you rely solely on the proc for aggro, no one is saying that. It means you get a additional aggro that makes up for the shortfall you get due to defensive DPS, being stunned a lot and having higher-damage classes hitting the mobs back. If you think you'll win a DPS fight with a rogue whilst defensive you are smoking something, one max backstab will make up for you 8 seconds of solo time.<br>
<br>
If you are happy with Skybreaker and think it's a better MT wep than a Willsapper then carry on using it. Personally I'll stick with my Willsapper and dream about EB proc weps. as for insults - it was you that questioned the ability of MT's that used high taunt proc weps. MT's of guilds that have killed mobs your guild will likely never kill use high taunt proc weps so how you can question that boggles my mind... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=1700.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=1700.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1700.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=1700.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=1700.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1700.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1700.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form 